The installation process will be made more user-friendly soon, hopefully. The main developer
currently uses Gentoo Linux and macOS High Sierra with Tomcat 6/7/8/9 and Oracle JDK 1.7/8.

Basic requirements:
- Linux or macOS or other Posix system
- Mercurial
- Java 1.7 SDK or higher
- Ant
- Servlet container (Tomcat 6 or higher)

Basic procedure is:
1. $ hg clone https://iovar.net/hg/iovar
2. $ cd iovar
3. $ ant project.install
4. $ ant app.install
5. $ ant app
6. Install webapp into servlet container ROOT context (the / context is assumed).
7. Start servlet container.
8. Open browser to http://localhost:8080/$ for the interactive shell interface.

Enjoy the web!

